      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1892_AS_RBH_2_00003"/>Hrn <hi rend="latintype">Doctor Richard</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Beer-Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb190427" type="place">I Wollzeile 15</rs></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><salute><pb facs="1892_AS_RBH_2_00004"/>Lieber Richard!</salute></opener><p><rs ref="#pmb18523" type="person">Paul Horn</rs> hat abge<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chrieben, ich theils bei
                  <hi rend="latintype">Frau <rs ref="#pmb16312" type="person">Fl.</rs></hi> mit.</p><p>Al<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>o morgen i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t nichts. –</p><p>Wann<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehn wir uns wieder? Ich kann in der <date>Sylve<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ternacht</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>pät ins <rs ref="#pmb49" type="place">Pfob</rs>,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>o um <time>2</time>. Herzlichst</p><closer>Ihr <signed>Arthur</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
